a8163_bequant_USP_icon_03.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="usp-icon-lottie _03"/></div><div class="usp-txt-con"><h3 class="txt h3 color-grey-100">Low video streaming quality and/or stalling</h3><div class="usp-p-txt-con"><p class="txt p color-grey-400">TCP Optimization can increase the speed of video streaming applications, which will increase their quality and reduce stalling situations.</p></div></div><div data-w-id="c5d135c0-8fed-a2a4-e5e2-3d90b9c24e83" style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0)" class="usp-bg"></div><div class="usp-number-con"><div class="txt mono color-grey-500">03</div></div></div><div class="usp-block"><div class="usp-image-con"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628bd935bf709b13cada8065/628bd935bf709b77d6da815f_bequant_USP_image_04.jpg" loading="lazy" alt="Abstract illustration of &quot;Latency issues in online gaming&quot;" class="usp-image"/><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628bd935bf709b13cada8065/628bd935bf709b784eda8164_bequant_USP_icon_04.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="usp-icon-lottie"/></div><div class="usp-txt-con"><h3 class="txt h3 color-grey-100">Latency issues in online gaming</h3><div class="usp-p-txt-con"><p class="txt p color-grey-400">Our bandwidth management can reduce latency in congestion situations, which will greatly benefit online gaming applications – leading to a reduction in gaming-related support inquiries.</p></div></div><div data-w-id="178f6aad-63f0-37bc-b9ec-ac12001cdb30" style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0)" class="usp-bg"></div><div class="usp-number-con"><div class="txt mono color-grey-500">04</div></div></div><div class="usp-block"><div class="usp-image-con"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628bd935bf709b13cada8065/628bd935bf709babc8da815d_bequant_USP_image_05.jpg" loading="lazy" alt="Abstract image of &quot;Abusive usage by subscribers&quot;" class="usp-image"/><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628bd935bf709b13cada8065/628bd935bf709b6f64da815e_bequant_USP_icon_05.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="usp-icon-lottie"/></div><div class="usp-txt-con"><h3 class="txt h3 color-grey-100">Abusive usage by subscribers</h3><div class="usp-p-txt-con"><p class="txt p color-grey-400">Our network visibility will let you see the top subscribers in your network, in terms of usage, and see the pattern of their usage, which may sometimes point to abusive usage patterns, or even virus problems.</p></div></div><div data-w-id="caea8c72-4cfa-01cb-9f44-f2e1283b3e40" style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0)" class="usp-bg"></div><div class="usp-number-con"><div class="txt mono color-grey-500">05</div></div></div><div class="usp-block"><div class="usp-image-con"><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628bd935bf709b13cada8065/628bd935bf709b7f37da815b_bequant_USP_image_06.jpg" loading="lazy" alt="Abstract image of &quot;No subscriber Quality of Experience measurements&quot;" class="usp-image"/><img src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628bd935bf709b13cada8065/628bd935bf709b45f5da8156_bequant_USP_icon_06.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="usp-icon-lottie"/></div><div class="usp-txt-con"><h3 class="txt h3 color-grey-100">No subscriber Quality of Experience measurements</h3><div class="usp-p-txt-con"><p class="txt p color-grey-400">The BQN Network Visibility provides measurements such as maximum subscriber speed and latency delivered over time, retransmissions and number of flows created and active – to help you characterize the quality you are delivering and diagnose possible problems.</p></div></div><div data-w-id="aa33fa97-d171-34bd-8ab1-67342db7d823" style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale3d(0, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0)" class="usp-bg"></div><div class="usp-number-con"><div class="txt mono color-grey-500">06</div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class="s-section cta"><div class="s-con cta"><div class="cta-colored-block bg-grey-700"><div class="cta-indent"><div id="distance" class="s-cta-quote-title"><h2 class="txt h2 color-grey-100">Maximizing the experience of internet users <span class="red-txt">—</span> making the most of network resources.</h2></div><div><a href="/about" class="button dark-on-dark write-02 w-inline-block"><div class="button-con"><div class="txt mono button-txt white-txt">about bequant</div><div class="button-arrow-con dark"><div data-is-ix2-target="1" class="btn-arrow-lottie" data-w-id="b12af041-1e29-af31-fc46-c3c5577f0d0e" data-animation-type="lottie" data-src="https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/628bd935bf709b13cada8065/628bd935bf709b72a4da8096_bequant_button-arrow.json" data-loop="0" data-direction="1" data-autoplay="0"